INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Cotton Australia Limited','https://cottonaustralia.com.au/','website','Cotton Australia is the not-for-profit peak representative body for the Australian cotton-growing industry, representing up to around 1,500 cotton farms mainly in New South Wales and Queensland. It is funded by a voluntary levy and advocates on industry, stewardship and natural resource management issues.','industry body');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Optimum Legal Solutions PTY LTD','https://www.optimumlegal.com.au/','website','Optimum Legal Solutions Pty Ltd is a Brisbane-based Queensland law firm (registered 2016) specialising in industrial relations, employment law, workplace safety, personal injury and HR advisory, acting for employers, employees and contractors.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Queensland Cricketers'' Club Limited','https://qcclub.com.au/','website','The Queensland Cricketers'' Club is a private social members'' club founded in 1959, located on the northern stand of the Gabba stadium in Woolloongabba, Brisbane. It offers members reserved stadium seating, dining, bars and function spaces for cricket and AFL events.','club');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Queensland Services, Industrial Union of Employees','https://www.theservicesunion.com.au/','website','Queensland Services, Industrial Union of Employees trades as The Services Union, a Queensland-registered trade union (ABN 13 540 483 194) covering workers in local government, energy, water, community services, travel, ports, clerical and related sectors. It is the Queensland (Services and Northern Administrative) branch of the Australian Services Union.','union');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Medibank Private Limited','https://www.medibank.com.au/','website','Medibank Private Limited is Australia''s largest private health insurer, headquartered in Melbourne, Victoria, and listed on the Australian Securities Exchange. Founded as a government insurer in 1976, it was privatised in 2014.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Sunlit Asian Supermarket Pty Ltd','https://www.sunlit.com.au/','website','Sunlit Asian Supermarket is an Asian grocery retail chain established in 2014 with multiple stores across Brisbane and the Gold Coast, Queensland, stocking ingredients and goods for Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Thai and Vietnamese cuisines.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('AWU S.A Branch','https://sa.awu.net.au/','website','The South Australian branch of The Australian Workers'' Union (AWU), one of Australia''s oldest trade unions, representing workers across many industries in South Australia.','union');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Beavis & Bartels Pty Ltd','https://beavisbartels.com.au/','website','A Queensland-based commercial plumbing and maintenance company (established 1954) specialising in large-scale hydraulic, drainage, gas-fitting and fire-safety work across Brisbane, the Gold Coast and Sunshine Coast.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Albert & Barbara Tucker Foundation','https://tuckerfoundation.org.au/','website','A Melbourne-based philanthropic foundation established under the will of Barbara Tucker that provides grants to charitable organisations, with a focus on public art galleries and museums, relief of poverty, youth scholarships, and animal welfare and environmental protection.','foundation');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Agtrade Holdings Pty Ltd','https://www.agtrade.com.au/','website','AgTrade is a Brisbane-headquartered global livestock, genetics, food security and biosecurity group whose businesses include Australian Rural Exports (AUSTREX), Paradigm Foods and Hay Australia; it was taken private by management-led investment in 2009.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Aletek Pty Ltd','https://www.aletek.com.au/','website','A family-owned Australian manufacturer (founded 2006, originating in Bundaberg, Queensland) of heavy-duty exhaust systems, thermal insulation blankets, diesel particulate filters and sound-suppression products for the mining, oil and gas, construction, marine and rail sectors.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Bundaberg Regional Irrigators Group Ltd','http://brig.org.au/','website','A not-for-profit organisation established in 2009 that represents and advocates for irrigators in the Bundaberg district of Queensland across commodities including sugar cane, grain and horticulture.','industry body');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Mining and Energy Union South Western District Branch','https://me.cfmeu.org.au/districts/nsw-south-western-district','website','The South Western District branch of the Mining and Energy Union (MEU), representing coal, metalliferous mining and energy workers in NSW from south of Sydney to the Victorian border and west to Broken Hill.','union');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Queensland Cane Agriculture &amp; Renewables Ltd','https://qcar.org.au/about/','website','Queensland Cane, Agriculture & Renewables (QCAR) is a member-based organisation representing sugarcane and broadacre growers in regions from Far North Queensland to northern New South Wales (formerly the Pioneer Cane Growers Organisation).','industry body');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Queensland Computers Pty Ltd','https://queenslandcomputers.com.au/','website','A Bundaberg-founded (2005) family-owned managed IT services and reseller business serving organisations across regional Queensland and northern NSW, offering managed IT, print, telephony, cloud and networking services.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Superior Pak Pty Ltd','https://www.superiorpak.com.au/','website','An Australian manufacturer and service provider of mobile waste collection and compaction equipment (front, rear and side loaders), founded in Brisbane in 1997 with a manufacturing centre in Bundaberg, Queensland.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Small Business Association of Australia Pty Ltd','https://smallbusinessassociation.com.au/','website','The Small Business Association of Australia (SBAA), a Queensland-based (Nerang) not-for-profit membership body that advocates for and provides support, education and services to micro, small and medium-sized businesses; it drafted Australia''s first Small Business Charter.','industry body');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('The Leadership Company Qld Pty Ltd','https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCre4uvvYgZFlWPSFsqfKQEA','website','A Queensland-based consultancy (registered 2012, Upper Mount Gravatt) specialising in leadership and organisational transformation, chaired and owned by former Queensland public-sector director-general Jim Varghese AM.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Your Accounting Partners Pty Ltd','https://youraccountingpartners.com.au/','website','An Australian accounting firm providing bookkeeping, accounting and compliance services to businesses across the ownership lifecycle.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Plumbing and Pipe Trades Union','https://www.ppteu.asn.au/','website','The Plumbing and Pipe Trades Employees Union (PPTEU), a federally registered trade union representing plumbing and pipe-trade workers across Australia, with branches covering Victoria, WA/NT, NSW/ACT and Queensland.','union');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Varley Group','https://varleygroup.com/','website','An Australian-owned engineering and manufacturing company founded in Newcastle in 1886, operating across defence and aerospace, specialised and electric vehicles, power services, marine, rail and telescopic towers, with subsidiaries including Norship and SEM Fire & Rescue.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('EJF Advisory Pty Ltd','https://abr.business.gov.au/ABN/View?id=91659678047','website','An Australian private company (advisory services) based in New South Wales, registered (ABN 91 659 678 047) and active from May 2022.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('ForHealth Group','https://www.forhealth.com.au/','website','An Australian healthcare operator (headquartered in Leichhardt, NSW) running a nationwide network of medical and dental centres and urgent-care clinics supporting independent doctors, dentists and allied health practitioners.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Australian Banking Association','https://www.ausbanking.org.au/','website','The trade association for the Australian banking industry (formerly the Australian Bankers'' Association), founded in 1985 and based in Sydney, with members including the major, regional and international banks operating in Australia.','industry body');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Origin Energy Limited','https://www.originenergy.com.au/','website','An ASX-listed (ASX:ORG) integrated energy company headquartered in Sydney that generates electricity and retails electricity, natural gas and LPG to millions of Australian customers; it was formed in 2000 as a spin-off from Boral.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Pario Solutions Group Pty Ltd','https://www.pariosolutions.com.au/','website','An Australian-owned consulting firm based in the ACT (registered 2008) providing governance, risk, business-systems, IT and disaster/emergency-management consulting services to the public sector and industry.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Add Staff Group','https://addstaff.com.au/','website','A Brisbane- and Melbourne-based recruitment, labour-hire and apprenticeship group founded in 2014 by Melissa Stanford, serving the electrotechnology, construction and trades sectors nationally.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Albert & Barbara Tucker','https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Albert_Tucker_(artist)','wikipedia','Albert Tucker (1914-1999) was a prominent Australian modernist painter and member of the Heide Circle and Angry Penguins movement; Barbara Tucker (nee Bilcock) was his wife and the manager of his artistic estate after his death.','other');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Initiative Capital Pty Ltd','https://www.dnb.com/business-directory/company-profiles.initiative_capital_pty_ltd.8c4fc7377f838976a2877a270f95bc39.html','website','Initiative Capital Pty Ltd is a Brisbane-based Australian private company (registered 2014) that develops large-scale land and infrastructure projects in water, food and energy, partnering with investment funds; its initiatives include the Urannah Water Scheme and Capricornia Energy Hub.','investment vehicle');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Southern Cross Transit (Qld) Pty Ltd','https://www.southerncrosstransit.com.au/','website','Southern Cross Transit is an Australian-owned family bus operator based at Karalee, near Ipswich in South East Queensland, providing contracted public transport, school bus, charter and coach-hire services. It is owned by the Oliveri family, who also run Interline Bus Services in NSW.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Hall Payne Lawyers Pty Ltd','https://hallpayne.com.au/','website','Hall Payne Lawyers is an Australian law firm headquartered in Brisbane with offices across Queensland, NSW, Victoria, Tasmania and the Northern Territory, specialising in employment and industrial law as well as personal injury, compensation and related areas.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('SDA Newcastle & Northern','https://www.actu.org.au/directory/shop-distributive-and-allied-employees-association-sda-newcastle-northern-nsw-branch/','website','The Newcastle & Northern branch of the Shop, Distributive and Allied Employees'' Association (SDA), the Australian trade union representing retail, fast-food and warehouse workers. The branch covers the Hunter and northern NSW and holds over 13,000 members.','union');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('HGH International Pty Ltd','https://hghinternational.com.au/','website','HGH International Pty Ltd is an Australian company (incorporated 2015) specialising in international product procurement for the construction and accommodation sectors, supplying builders with materials and joinery packages for hotels, resorts, student accommodation and aged-care facilities.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('The Star Entertainment Qld Limited','https://www.starentertainmentgroup.com.au/','website','The Star Entertainment Qld Limited is the Queensland operating subsidiary of The Star Entertainment Group (ASX: SGR), Australia''s largest listed casino and integrated-resort operator, running The Star Gold Coast and The Star Brisbane casinos.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Southern Oil Refining Pty Ltd','https://sor.com.au/','website','Southern Oil Refining (SOR) is a 100% Australian-owned company based in Wagga Wagga, NSW, that re-refines waste lubricating oil back into base lube oils and produces other fuels, processing a significant share of Australia''s annual waste lube oil.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('RIoT Solutions Pty Ltd','https://riotsolutions.com.au/','website','RIoT Solutions is a Brisbane-based Australian managed cyber-security and IT/OT network services provider serving government and enterprise clients. It is now part of the Orro group.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Rocklea Auto Parts Pty Ltd','https://www.rockleaautoparts.com.au/','website','Rocklea Auto Parts is a Brisbane-based automotive parts supplier and vehicle dismantler/wrecker in Rocklea, Queensland, selling new and used parts and specialising in late-model Kia, Hyundai, Volkswagen and 4x4 vehicles.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('VBR Lawyers Pty Ltd','https://vbrlaw.com.au/','website','VBR Lawyers is a Queensland-based compensation law firm practising exclusively in personal injury law, including motor vehicle, workers'' compensation, asbestos/dust disease, medical negligence and institutional abuse claims, with offices in Brisbane and the Gold Coast.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Lavarch Productions Pty Ltd','https://www.lavarchproductions.com.au/','website','Lavarch Productions is an Australian documentary film production company run by Michael Lavarch (a former federal Attorney-General) and Larissa Behrendt, producing documentaries focused on Australian Indigenous culture, history and social justice.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('AusVeg Ltd','https://ausveg.com.au/','website','AUSVEG is the national peak industry body representing Australian vegetable, potato and onion growers, advocating to government and administering grower levies invested in industry research and development.','industry body');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Axis Plumbing NSW Group Pty Ltd','https://www.axisplumbing.com.au/','website','Axis Plumbing NSW Group (part of Axis Services Group, founded 1994) is a hydraulic/plumbing, mechanical and fire-services contractor for large commercial construction and maintenance projects, with its NSW base at Padstow.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Optimum Legal Solutions Pty Ltd','https://www.optimumlegal.com.au/','website','Optimum Legal Solutions is a Brisbane-based Australian law firm (registered 2016) specialising in industrial relations, employment law and HR advisory, also offering injury compensation, superannuation, wills and estate services.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('The Ethnic Communities Council of Queensland Limited','https://eccq.com.au/','website','The Ethnic Communities Council of Queensland (ECCQ), established 1976, is the independent member-based peak body representing multicultural communities across Queensland and the state council of the Federation of Ethnic Communities'' Councils of Australia, also delivering health, aged-care and community programs.','other');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('National Rugby League','https://www.nrl.com/about-us/','website','The National Rugby League (NRL) is the premier professional rugby league competition in Australia and New Zealand, administered by the Australian Rugby League Commission, which is the governing body for the sport in Australia.','other');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Shine Lawyers Pty Ltd','https://www.shine.com.au/about-us','website','Shine Lawyers is an Australian personal-injury and compensation law firm founded in Toowoomba in 1976, operating on a no-win-no-fee basis across Australia and New Zealand. It is part of ASX-listed Shine Justice Ltd (ASX: SHJ).','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Windlab Pty Limited','https://www.windlab.com/','website','Windlab is an Australian renewable-energy company (founded 2003) that develops wind, solar and battery energy projects using CSIRO-derived wind-resource modelling technology, with projects including the Kennedy Energy Park in north Queensland.','company');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Association of Labor Lawyers (Queensland) Incorporated','https://qldlaborlawyerscom.wordpress.com/executivecommittee/','website','The Association of Labor Lawyers (Queensland) is a Queensland membership association of lawyers and others who support Australian Labor Party principles, aiming to advance Labor policy and promote reform of the law, justice administration and legal services.','professional body');
INSERT INTO "donor_info" VALUES('Springfield City Group','https://greaterspringfield.com.au/about-us/','website','Springfield City Group (formerly Springfield Land Corporation), founded in 1992 by Maha Sinnathamby and Bob Sharpless, is the private master-planned property developer behind Greater Springfield near Ipswich, Queensland, Australia''s first privately built city.','company');
