INSERT INTO "position" VALUES(820,'queensland-tim-nicholls-clayfield','health','Queensland Minister for Health and Ambulance Services (Crisafulli LNP government, since November 2024). Secured a record $33.1 billion health budget in June 2025, including $18.5 billion for the government''s ''Hospital Rescue Plan'' to build three new hospitals and expand ten others, delivering more than 2,600 new beds statewide, plus a Queensland Cancer Centre and an additional 4,500 frontline health workers in 2025-26.',1);
